data.title: Qlik on LinkedIn: How enterprises are investing in tech to succeed with gen AI
data.meta_description: Take it from Qlik’s James Fisher: a trusted data foundation fuels the insights and advanced use cases where the power of #GenerativeAI and traditional #AI…
data.text: #CelebratingSuccess with the Qlik Web Team led by AnnaMae Wilson, alongside Omer Arman, Annie Ho and Michael Marquis, who won our 'We Succeed Together' Core Values Award at our recent Town Hall. The web team delivered a brand new, optimized website that reflects a best-in-class experience and incorporated our new branding and Talend products. This undertaking could have taken 12-18 months to complete, but with support from many cross-functional teams, this team delivered the work in less than seven months. Qlik CEO Mike Capone commented: "What these folks and their teams were able to deliver together – in partnership with marketing, legal, strategy, and the business – was an incredible feat." Fantastic achievement from everyone involved! #WeAreHiring! For more about #LifeAtQlik and opportunities to #JoinOurQlik, go to https://bit.ly/qlikcareers or reach out to start a conversation.
